│ %R0, 255`) should be simplified to `true`, not `false`. The optimizer is getting the result exactly backward.                                                                            │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ This points to a logic error in how the `samesign` and `nsw` information is being combined. I will look for the implementation of `isImpliedCondition` in `ValueTracking.cpp`.           │
